. {ndash} Vi m\u00e5 vise samarbeidspartnerne v\u00e5re at vi er teknologisk p\u00e5 toppen. Det holder ikke med vakker Oppdalsnatur, sier Jan Kleven. Her jobber Wenche Stensheim med pakkingen av esker."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f2bff2cdebc48b9b00ae4b3b66cd7c575b83ec47538de9c20099c92cd158931a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T10:30:30.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- For tre \u00e5r siden fikk jeg en bonus p\u00e5 ti millioner kroner - fordelt p\u00e5 tre \u00e5r - for innsatsen min i Elotec. Det setter b\u00e5de jeg og familien min pris p\u00e5."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1147604.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Elotec-2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/317c7558e210b601ab2b7e0dc82762f6a4729fd3.jpg?597765de"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Kleven setter pris p\u00e5 l\u00f8nna -adressa.no", "Burde v\u00e6rt femteplass", "\u00c5pen stil"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "317c7558e210b601ab2b7e0dc82762f6a4729fd3"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "business"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["finansavisen", "general electric"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["l\u00f8nn", "kroner", "millioner", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["europas", "elotec", "elizabeths", "oppdalsnatur", "adresseavisen", "oppdalbedriften og kleven", "silicon valley"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["windsor", "england